Okay, so as you can see in this project,
the first thing your app will access is
the index file (the main file).
The index file will take you to the
navigation folder and allow you to
navigate between screens.
The first screen that will appear is the
home screen, and from the home screen,
you can use the navigation to navigate
to other screens.
You should know that your screens will
be using the components, context, and
hooks folders as their missing pieces of
the puzzle. This means that instead of
writing all the code in one file, we are
dividing it into clearly named folders and
files
